FIELD OBSERVATIONS: Both of our specimens of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1901" box="[772,1025,1651,1674]" class="Mammalia" family="Emballonuridae" genus="Saccopteryx" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="40" pageNumber="40" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="gymnura">
